# Circle Video Management and View Options

This plan addresses video management for owners and enhanced viewing options for all users.

## Proposed Changes

### [Hook] useCircleVideos
#### [MODIFY] [useCircleVideos.ts](file:///c:/Users/elink/./.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/hooks/useCircleVideos.ts)
- Add `deleteVideo` mutation:
  - Deletes the video record from `circle_videos`.
  - Invalides `['circle-videos', circleId]`.
- Add `updateVideo` mutation:
  - Updates title, description, is_premium, price, and playlist_id.
  - Optionally updates the thumbnail image.

### [Component] CircleVideoCard
#### [MODIFY] [CircleVideoCard.tsx](file:///c:/Users/elink/./.gemini/antigravity/scratch/MomNest/heart-lens-studio-main/src/components/circles/CircleVideoCard.tsx)
